data.description: Great price on this sound side beach cottage located on a high lot in Archers Creek. Only 4 lots from one of Emerald Isle's  public sound accesses and very close to the beach, shopping, and restaurants! Enjoy easy living in this house that has Juniper siding which never needs to be painted & boasts natural beach landscaping that requires minimal yard work if any.  Open living concept on main level w/ bedroom & bath. 2 more bedrooms (each with its own private access to second story sun deck), full bath, walk-in-storage, and office nook upstairs.  FEATURES:2 heated/cooled ground level rooms w/ rough-ins for expansion, hurricane slide-in shutters, security system, upgraded heating & air unit, screened side porch, covered front porch, ample parking in rear of home, outside hot/cold shower etc.
